<p><div class="lightbox-wrapper"><a class="lightbox" href="https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/original/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a.png" data-download-href="/uploads/short-url/4F9ulslKPgDgHD6bHQjMMH12i4W.png?dl=1" title="CleanShot 2021-11-22 at 10.51.25@2x"><img src="https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/optimized/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a_2_690x239.png" alt="CleanShot 2021-11-22 at 10.51.25@2x" data-base62-sha1="4F9ulslKPgDgHD6bHQjMMH12i4W" width="690" height="239" srcset="https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/optimized/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a_2_690x239.png, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/optimized/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a_2_1035x358.png 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/optimized/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a_2_1380x478.png 2x" data-small-upload="https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/redash1/optimized/2X/2/20af984d36fe9f0ee78e91714f187db9ed13571a_2_10x10.png"><div class="meta">
